flowchart TD
    A([Candidate scheduled for assessment]) --> B[Staff performs one-time identity check<br/>photo and ID document]
    B --> C{Identity accepted?}
    C -- No --> D[Candidate refused / rescheduled]
    C -- Yes --> E[Assessment begins]
    E --> F[Supervisor observes many webcam feeds<br/>attention divided / intermittent]
    E --> G[Session recorded for later review]
    F --> H{Overt suspicious<br/>behaviour seen?}
    H -- No --> I[Assessment continues unmonitored<br/>subtle misconduct may go undetected]
    H -- Yes --> J[Supervisor writes informal note<br/>no standard rubric]
    I --> K([Assessment ends])
    J --> K
    G --> K
    K --> L[Recording reviewed only if<br/>misconduct suspected]
    L --> M{Misconduct confirmed?}
    M -- Uncertain --> N[Subjective judgment<br/>inconsistent across supervisors]
    M -- Yes --> O[Result flagged / queried / invalidated]
    N --> P[Ad hoc email or call to candidate / client<br/>weak, non-timestamped evidence]
    O --> P
    P --> Q([Outcome recorded manually])
